data.description: Wonderful 3/2/2 starter home. Quiet area offers many updates/improvements! You'll love the spacious, open kitchen/dining area-adjacent to sunroom for entertaining! Kitchen remodeled w/new cabinetry, flooring, counters, appliances & fixtures- 2010; New roof 2012; hot water heater 2014; plumbing 2012; sewer line 2010; front door 2011; master bath- tile flooring, shower enlarged/remodeled 2010/2011; sunroom- exterior siding replaced w/vinyl siding 2012. Large backyard w/storage, patio, & alley access.
